Package: svyflow
Title: Survey-Design-Aware Descriptive Analysis Driven by an Analysis Plan
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given  = "Farhad",
           family = "Nabizada",
           role   = c("aut", "cre"),
           email  = "farhad.nabizada@atr-consulting.com")
Description: Produces design-correct descriptive statistics (proportions,
    means, totals, quantiles, min, max) for survey data driven by an
    analysis-plan data frame. Estimates use the 'srvyr' / 'survey' engine
    so weights, strata and clusters are respected; standard errors and
    95% confidence intervals are reported alongside point estimates.
    Handles Kobo / SurveyCTO style multi-select variables, single and
    double disaggregation, and is built to be extended with output
    formatters (Excel, HTML, etc.) in later releases.
